articles.title: Canadian woman found dead surrounded by dingoes on Australian beach - BBC
articles.description: Local police have yet to determine whether the 19-year-old tourist died from drowning after going for a swim or was attacked by the animals.
articles.content:
A 19-year-old Canadian woman has been found dead, with her body surrounded by a pack of dingoes on a popular Australian beach, according to local officials.
